<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playball&family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo-removebg-preview.png">
  <style>
    /* Internal CSS - Same as refactored version */
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }

    header {
      background: white;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .logo h2 {
      font-family: 'Playball', cursive;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
    }

    nav a {
      margin-left: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    nav a.active,
    nav a:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 183, 1, 0.376);
    }

    .hero {
      background-image: url('/images/restaurant222.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      height: 370px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 60px;
      opacity: 0.14;
    }

    .hero h3 {
      color: rgba(250, 180, 5, 0.783);
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(70, 70, 70, 0.783);
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .about-section {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 50px 30px;
      justify-content: space-around;
    }

    .about-text,
    .about-benefits {
      flex: 1 1 300px;
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .about-text h3,
    .about-benefits h3 {
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .about-text p,
    .about-benefits ul {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .about-image img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 350px;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .about-benefits ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .location {
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .location p {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
    }

    .location a {
      color: rgb(32, 32, 59);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-decoration-color: rgba(250, 180, 5, 0.783);
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 576px) {
      nav {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      nav a {
        margin-left: 0;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 40px;
      }

      .about-section {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/images/logo-removebg-preview.png" alt="Tomi's Kitchen Logo">
      <h2>Tomi's Kitchen</h2>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
      <a href="/about" class="nav-link active">About</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="nav-link">Contacts</a>
      <a href="/menu" class="nav-link">Our Menus</a>
      <a href="/book" class="nav-link">Book A Table</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About us</h1>
    <h3>WHY CHOOSE US?</h3>
    <p>Best foods for you and your family.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-text">
      <h3>10 Years Of Experience In Restaurant Services</h3>
      <p>
        Tomi's Kitchen is a restaurant that was established in March 2014.
        We started as a small cafe serving pastries, cakes, and snacks. The restaurant later expanded its menu to include Nigerian and continental dishes.<br><br>
        Tomi's Kitchen aims to meet customers' needs and ensure maximum satisfaction.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-image">
      <img src="/images/about-img.jpg" alt="Restaurant interior">
    </div>

    <div class="about-benefits">
      <h3>We care about the health and well-being of our customers</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Fresh ingredients and products</li>
        <li>Professional & skilled chefs</li>
        <li>Best offers and low-cost services</li>
        <li>Vegan cuisines</li>
        <li>Online booking system</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="location">
    <p>
      We are located inside Federal College Of Animal Health And Production Technology, Ibadan, Oyo State, Nigeria.
      <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Federal+College+Ibadan+Nigeria" target="_blank">Our Location</a>
    </p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
